CSS Flexbox Center:
.container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}

CSS Grid Layout:
.grid-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
}

